U.K. Stocks Erase Their Earlier Advance; Marks & Spencer, Next Decline

-- B y   A n d r e w   R u m m e r
-- 
2011-07-13T11:16:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-13/u-k-stocks-erase-their-earlier-advance-marks-spencer-next-decline.html
U.K. stocks erased their gains as
Marks & Spencer Group Plc and Next Plc declined. The FTSE 100
rose less than 0.1 percent to 5,871.51 at 12:14 a.m. in  London ,
having earlier climbed as much as 0.5 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
